      "content": "but a budget doesnt change the math. every month we just fall further behind. it’s not just about the money, it’s just... everything about me feels like a failure. if i wasn't here, the extra income they'd have, the lack of stress, the freedom from worrying about me... it almost seems like the only logical way to actually help them.",
